cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.IR. 

The paper is about person re-identification, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a new loss function for training deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning, specifically deep learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The paper also deals with large-scale datasets and surveillance cameras, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
